<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="considerable-adj">considerable <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'sɪdərəbl/    美 /kən'sɪdərəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(数量、程度、重要性等) 相当大的</strong></h4>
<p>great in amount, size, importance, etc. (significant)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a considerable expense / difference
一大笔费用/相当大的差异</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a considerable person / problem
重要的人/问题</p></div></div>